caption: I go with my wife to this lovely place quite a bit! This is my favorite spot to to have a good dinner.  I visit this spot at least once a month. The food is fantastic, the staff members are professional and the cost is decent. I enjoy being in this place over a tasty meal.

The New York style pizza was sooooo yummy ! Not only was the pizza delicious but the guava cheese fried Oreos were the best, there’s no other like them. Will for sure be ordering delivery from here again!
Fry Haus is amazing!! Unique and creative concept with lots of fried goodness😍😍😍 I loved all the items that I have tried and will definitely be back
